data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 full bath house features a large backyard with a privacy fence, huge open living room with a gorgeous stone fireplace, barrel ceiling in the kitchen, and at the end of a cul-de-sac. In the last three years it has NEW gutters, fence, roof, fixtures, ceiling fans, water heater, and stove. Beautiful community pool with lifeguard on duty.  Call today to see this home.
